{
  "stem": "5970.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my mother was actually liberated by the Russians in Auschwitz, at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't know it at the time, but she was left behind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we went on this awful march from Auschwitz that was well-documented and described and written about, where we walked and walked and walked in the snow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the road--- the snow was red, because on both sides of the road there were bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Whoever couldn't walk was shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we just, we-- I don't know how long it took, but more than, I think, about three days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At night, we-- we were told to just sit down for the night somewhere, and-- and the rest we walked.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's quite a long way from Auschwitz to Breslau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We walked till then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was the most dreadful thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You wanted, actually, to drop everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You didn't have anything, but we had some bread, which we found on the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "A-- a cart of bread was turned over, and so we each grabbed a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we-- it was difficult to carry it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You-- you get so tired walking and-- and marching.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- and it was-- but we held onto this bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was practically carried by two other women, and it was-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was dreadful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the road-- I-- I just visualize it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I remember it like it was yesterday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "All we heard was this crackling of-- of guns shooting, the dogs with the guards, people lying on both sides of the road.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And us just going along.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and if you stayed behind, you were shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the guards were changing, but we didn't change.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had relief.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
